headline: What to Expect in Markets This Week: Investors Watching Developments in Iran, Awaiting Jobs Report, Other Economic Data, Earnings Reports
summary: Market participants will be keeping close tabs on developments in Iran after the U.S. and Israel launched strikes over the weekend, while awaiting a slew of economic reports, highlighted by the scheduled release Friday of the February jobs report.
